00:07:23.520 --> 00:07:28.460
My book, "Madison's Hand: Revising
the Constitutional Convention",

00:07:28.460 --> 00:07:30.800
is a biography of Madison's notes

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:34.190
on the Constitutional
Convention of 1787.

00:07:34.190 --> 00:07:37.970
And it's a story about how
Madison originally wrote,

00:07:37.970 --> 00:07:41.070
and then revised his notes as
he changed his understanding

00:07:41.070 --> 00:07:44.700
of the Convention, the
Constitution, and his own role.

00:07:44.700 --> 00:07:49.150
It's a book that argues
that Madison wrote only part

00:07:49.150 --> 00:07:53.480
of his iconic notes
in the summer of 1787.

00:07:53.480 --> 00:07:56.600
I argue he finished
them two years later

00:07:56.600 --> 00:07:59.400
when Thomas Jefferson
returned from France.

00:07:59.400 --> 00:08:03.170
And he then continued to revise
them throughout his life.

00:08:03.170 --> 00:08:09.600
It's a book that argues Madison
even replaced some key speeches

00:08:09.600 --> 00:08:14.130
to better accord with Jefferson's
new Republican politics.

00:08:14.130 --> 00:08:17.300
It's not the book I
set out to write.

00:08:17.300 --> 00:08:22.470
And so today, I will tell the story
behind the book, and the mysteries,

00:08:22.470 --> 00:08:25.260
investigations, and questions.

00:08:25.260 --> 00:08:28.710
I began the book in 2008

00:08:28.710 --> 00:08:34.410
and I unfortunately repressed how
difficult I found it to write.

00:08:34.410 --> 00:08:36.830
I recently reread some
emails I wrote to people

00:08:36.830 --> 00:08:39.340
who serve as coaches and critics.

00:08:39.340 --> 00:08:43.680
"Am I going to be seen as a nut?

00:08:43.680 --> 00:08:47.300
I can't figure out how
to arrange the material.

00:08:47.300 --> 00:08:50.620
I bump into puzzles at every turn.

00:08:50.620 --> 00:08:53.790
A snappy subtitle escapes me.

00:08:53.790 --> 00:08:58.130
I have no idea who will
possibly read this.

00:08:58.130 --> 00:09:04.830 position:56%
And my editor is forcing me to spend
the weekend shaving 7,000 words

00:09:04.830 --> 00:09:09.700
out of the evidence section,
and she is completely right."

00:09:09.700 --> 00:09:14.340
But one thing I have always
remembered is the extraordinary

00:09:14.340 --> 00:09:18.620
assistance given to me by the
outstanding staff of the Library.

00:09:18.620 --> 00:09:22.600 position:56%
And one page of the acknowledgements
