00:48:57.190 --> 00:49:01.830
For myself, I find that Madison
has been given a pass that's quite

00:49:01.830 --> 00:49:04.650
interesting compared to
other people like Jefferson,

00:49:04.650 --> 00:49:09.070
who I personally think he agreed
with much more than we realize.

00:49:09.070 --> 00:49:12.530
Montpelier does a wonderful
job talking about slavery,

00:49:12.530 --> 00:49:16.020
and they actually have a wonderful
room there when you visit.

00:49:16.020 --> 00:49:18.280
For most of Madison's -- certainly

00:49:18.280 --> 00:49:21.560
