actually so shocking to the man

00:50:18.730 --> 00:50:21.910
who had worked for many
years with him as a secretary

00:50:21.910 --> 00:50:25.870
that he originally thought
that Madison's will was forged.

00:50:25.870 --> 00:50:30.500 position:56%
And so but Madison actually -- other
than being against the slave trade,

00:50:30.500 --> 00:50:35.160
which he is against when it becomes
clear that everybody's against it,

00:50:35.160 --> 00:50:40.750 position:56%
I think he was not -- I don't know
why he's given such a pass about it.

00:50:40.750 --> 00:50:46.180
And in the Virginia Ratification
