00:53:23.810 --> 00:53:28.080
The Supreme Court, in terms of its
majority opinions in recent years,

00:53:28.080 --> 00:53:34.490
has been very careful to keep
distanced from the notes.

00:53:34.490 --> 00:53:37.450
This isn't so true of the late
19th Century Supreme Court,

00:53:37.450 --> 00:53:41.520
so there are cases involving
