secret or confidential,

00:58:51.000 --> 00:58:57.830
and they actually meant -- were
really meaning confidential.

00:58:57.830 --> 00:59:01.650
So people write things
that are illusions

00:59:01.650 --> 00:59:06.810
to what's going to happen at best.

00:59:06.810 --> 00:59:12.460 position:56%
And so we have -- other than these
sort of private legislative diaries,

00:59:12.460 --> 00:59:14.960
we don't have a lot
of correspondents

00:59:14.960 --> 00:59:18.870
that explicitly says the
day-to-day accounts the way we do

00:59:18.870 --> 00:59:22.470
for the first Congress where
