00:59:46.450 --> 00:59:51.040
And we don't know what's destroyed.

00:59:51.040 --> 00:59:53.860
We know that Dolley Madison's
niece destroys some things.

00:59:53.860 --> 00:59:58.150
She was told she was supposed
to destroy some things.

00:59:58.150 --> 01:00:01.350
So we know -- I think
particularly descendants --

01:00:01.350 --> 01:00:05.080
particularly I think interesting
wives and daughters did do some

01:00:05.080 --> 01:00:06.380
of that in concern with reputation.

01:00:06.380 --> 01:00:07.680 position:56%
People -- some of Madison's notes --

01:00:07.680 --> 01:00:08.980
there are several letters that
